[2] Ukraine
Date: Mon 4 Mar 2019
Source: Outbreak News Today [abridged, edited]
http://outbreaknewstoday.com/measles-ukraine-9th-fatality-reported-35654/


Ukrainian health officials reported an additional 2751 measles infections during the past week, bringing the outbreak total for 2019 to 24 042 (10 588 adults and 13 454 children).

In addition, a 9th measles death was reported a 57-year-old woman from Kiev.

Lviv, Vinnytsya and Rivne have seen the most cases year to date. In the Lviv region, 19 671 children were vaccinated in the month of [February 2019]. Similar events are already taking place in Vinnytsia region which were initiated by local authorities.

[Byline: Robert Herriman]

